  "text": "IVY-VE supports these aims by fusing web-based technologies with Second Life. Through the use of web technologies we offer intuitive means of managing scenarios and resources within the 3D environment. Our implementation approach follows an Agile methodology [CITATION_1] , evaluating our prototypes in iterations. For that purpose we present a critical evaluation of our prototype as well.",
